cz.cuni.mff.kocur.decisions

Class Target

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.kocur.decisions.Target

  • public class Target
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represents a target, that we will be using in our decisions. Target can be a location, entity, item, name or ability stored inside. These are all the things we can care about.
    Author:
    kocur
